title: Artemis Fowl 1-6 Audio Books FIXED
description:
These are the Audio books to the Artemis Fowl Series by Eoin Colfer, and all are read by Nathaniel Parker. FIXED.

I have split each book up into their chapters. I've grown tired of audio books and them being broken up in random places. In the original files, there were almost 100 or way over 100 files, and I joined files, and split files to make it so that there was one file per chapter.

As far as I have been able to tell, there hasn't really been anything wrong with these files from the beginning except for the sixth book where I had to take out the "End of Disk 1, Disk 2" audios. But, if you find something the matter, just comment and I'll try and fix what is wrong.

I've also made each book into an .m4b (audio book format) file. These are actually smaller in size, and they work perfectly on your iPod.

If you can think of anything else that needs to be fixed, or if there is a problem with any of the files, just comment, and I'll try and fix the problem.

Enjoy.
